==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Forspent
<hw>For*spent"</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[AS.
<ets>forspendan</ets> to consume; pref. <ets>for-</ets> +
<ets>spendan</ets> to spend.]</ety> <def>Wasted in strength; tired;
exhausted.</def> <mark>[Archaic]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>A gentleman almost <qex>forspent</qex> with speed.</q>
<rj><qau>Shak.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Forstall</ent>⟦br⟧
